               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18120219-47-cd281" type="crimeDate">10th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120219-47-off280 t18120219-47-cd281"></join>, eighteen yards of ribbon, value 4 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18120219-47-victim447" type="victimName">
                     Samuel 
                     Oliver
                  <interp inst="t18120219-47-victim447" type="surname" value="Oliver"></interp>
